      "text": "練習の時よりさらに球威が上がってるんじゃないか\n……おーいさくら、コースを喋ったら打たれるぞ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The ball is even faster than during practice.\n…Hey‚ Sakura‚ if you say where you aim‚ the batters will hit it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
