      "text": "（さくら達が1対0で勝ち越しているけど）\n（最後のイニングでツーアウト満塁か……マズいな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Even though Sakura’s team is winning 1-0…）\n（…it’s the last inning with two outs and the bases loaded… This is bad.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
