      "text": "（打たれた！　ライト方面、ホームランか！？）\n（いや、フェンスギリギリで捕ったぞ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hit! To right field‚ is it a home run?!）\n（No‚ they caught it just before the fence!）",
        "id": ""
      },
