      "text": "これでスリーアウトだから……あれ？　勝った？\n私達の勝ち！？　みんな、やったね！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that’s three outs… Huh? We won?\nWe really won?! Everyone‚ we did it!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.1264849662,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.306481533
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
