      "text": "（練習試合、それもたった三イニングだけだけど）\n（全員がさくらを囲んであんなに喜んで……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It was just a practice game‚ and only three innings…）\n（…but everyone is so happy‚ surrounding Sakura like that.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.8175093014
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "今日は本当に頑張ったね！\n次は私が、ライブ頑張るからね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You all did great today!\nNext‚ it’s my turn to do my best at the live show!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.7175093014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "さくらも部員達も、みんないい笑顔だな……\n……ちょっと、胴上げはストップ！　危ないから！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura and the team members all have such great smiles…\n…Wait‚ stop lifting her! It’s dangerous!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3333363851,
      "sfxList": []
