      "text": "{user}さん、もうすぐ本番ですね\nリハも完璧でしたし、準備万端です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ it’s almost showtime.\nThe rehearsal was perfect‚ and we’re all ready to go!",
        "id": ""
      },
