      "text": "……あ！　ソフトボール部のみんなの寄せ書きだ！\n「絶対、ライブ観に行くから、頑張って」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah! It’s a message from everyone on the softball team!\n“We’ll definitely come see the live show‚ so good luck!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.7352196852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
