      "startTime": 157.1018700759
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "彼女達もさくらのファンになったらしくてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Apparently they became Sakura fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.1018700759,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_03-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、試合を通じて友情が芽生えるなんて\n青春って感じで、なんだか嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ to think that a friendship blossomed through a game…\nit feels like a youth drama‚ I’m so happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.9192807834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.2525886854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
