      "text": "あ、これは練習試合の応援に来てほしいって\nお手紙を送ってくれた部員さんからのメッセージです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ this is a message from the team member who\nsent me a letter asking me to come cheer for their practice game.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.4192553521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
