      "text": "「さくらちゃんと一緒にプレイ出来て\nソフトボールがますます好きになりました」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“I love softball even more now‚\nbecause I was able to play with Sakura-chan.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.5525886854,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 188.3859220188
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
