      "text": "「いつかさくらちゃんに私のニュースが届くくらいの\n日本一の凄い選手になってみせます」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Someday‚ I’ll become a great player‚ the best in Japan‚\nso that Sakura-chan will hear about me.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.1192553521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 195.7192553521
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
