    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "（観客席に何を見つけたんだ？　……あれは、横断幕？）\n（昨日の部員達か……。良かったな、さくら）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（What did she see in the audience? …Is that a banner?）\n（They are the team members from yesterday… Good for you‚ Sakura.）",
