      "text": "今度は私が頑張るから、応援よろしくお願いします！\n――どっちが先に日本一になるか、競争だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now it’s my turn to do my best‚ so please cheer me on!\n――It's a competition to see who becomes the best in Japan first!",
        "id": ""
      },
